    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\Tutorial\Client\BB\WallTool_01.png">2f7d0004:00000000:2b12bed659b8e83b</T>
      <T n="text">0x243A99A6<!--String: "Click on the Rooms and Walls catalog and choose the Empty Rooms sort to find the Wall Tool. Use the Wall Tool to draw individual walls. The cost for placement is attached to the top of the Wall Tool as you drag.\n\nNote: There is also a Room Tool that you can use to draw custom rooms."--></T>
